  <ul>
    <li>
      Led as my team's designated frontend domain expert in the transformation of a multi-million line long enterprise insurance application from Visual Basic to Typescript and React.
    </li>
    <li>
      Contributed to domain-level security auditing of backend APIs and authored end to end API tests in C#.
    </li>
    <li>
      Took ownership of refinement and triaging of large frontend technical initiatives for my team -  identifying key technical roadblocks, drafting acceptance criteria, and supporting enhancements to shared libraries to unblock development.
    </li>
  </ul>
