    </li>
    <li>
      Acted as the frontend domain expert on an R&D initiative to share multi-step workflows across multiple acquired warehouse logistics applications, with the goal being to consolidate those applications into a single platform.
    </li>
    <li>
      Acted as the primary frontend liaison for Flexport ( partner business ) in the development of a new embedded application with Shopify's CMS. Collaborated closely with the Shopify core-library developers and ecosystems teams, and leveraged learnings to unblock Flexport's engineers on technical hurdles in the release of the Flexport app.
    </li>
    <li>
      Led an initiative introduce Storybook across all Shopify Logistics codebases, enabling several hundred engineers to make visual changes to Shopify Logistics applications without running the full Shopify codebase end to end. Integrated Storybook into existing CI pipelines to automatically deploy branches for demoing work with product design teams.
    </li>
    <li>
      Volunteered as a mentor in Shopify's mentor/mentee pairing program.
    </li>
  </ul>
  <h3>
    Healthgrades - Senior Software Engineer
  </h3>
  <p>
    <strong>
      2019 - 2022, Denver CO &amp; Remote
